{
  "stem": "3638.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that was the first-- first week of-- first, second week during-- in the beginning of the war.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't give anybody a chance to sell it or to hide it, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Happened right through it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What could he do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He couldn't do very much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He-- if you would-- if you would resist them, they-- they had-- they had guns with them, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How could you resist it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You were lucky that they leave you alone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no resistance.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You couldn't do-- you couldn't resist it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You couldn't demand anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The only thing my father did, after the first raid, they left something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So what he did, we had a hiding place where-- behind the sh-- behind the premises somewhere, where it was a-- a room where you couldn't-- you couldn't get in.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They-- nobody knew about the room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that's where we hide a lot of food and produce for ourselves, not for selling purposes, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we were- we were lucky that we could still-- there was no bread available, so we had flour.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We baked the bread, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was September.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It went on till 1940, the beginning of '41.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's when we went to Velichka.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was carrying on very limited, limited.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was nothing for sale, but he still managed to buy something and to sell, because we had a lot of contacts.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A lot of-- a lot of the Polish peasant were-- what you call it-- they had-- they used to buy from us on credit.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was-- he had a lot of-- they had a lot of credit with us, which they didn't pay.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they gave us something, you know, to keep us going.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it wasn't-- we could survive.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
